data.description: Upgrades abound in this immaculate, paired home in coveted Whispering Pines.  This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home will impress from the moment you enter.  The open floor plan, soaring 10ft high ceilings and beautiful engineered hardwood floors provide an inviting and comfortable main floor.  In addition, this level boasts an upgraded, high-end kitchen with newer Kitchen Aid appliances, double oven, cooktop(gas hookup available), granite counters and custom coffee bar. The kitchen leads to a custom pantry/laundry room.  This home also offers a convenient and spacous office adjacent to the kitchen/living room. A cozy covered patio is located right off the dining room and offers durable epoxy flooring.The luxurious primary suite offers upgraded bath flooring, extra large shower stall and custom walk-in closet system. Rounding out the main floor, the home offers a large guest bedroom with adjacent full hallway bath.  As you move to the custom basement, this home offers 2 additional bedrooms (1 non-conforming) and another full bath.  In addition, there is a generous family room and an abundance of closets and storage. Whispering Pines provides a lifestyle that is second to none, with great views, wonderful amenities, all in a stunning setting.  This home will not disappoint!
